'''2020年歐洲足球錦標賽'''（{{lang-en|'''UEFA EURO 2020'''}}，通稱'''2020年歐國盃'''）是第16屆[[欧洲足球锦标赛|歐洲國家盃]]。歐洲國家盃是由[[歐洲足球協會聯盟|歐洲足球協會聯盟]]（UEFA）主办的、由来自[[欧洲|欧洲]]的男子国家[[足球|足球]]队参与的四年一度的[[杯赛|杯赛]]。<ref name="regulations0">{{Cite web|title=Regulations of the UEFA European Football Championship 2018–20|url=https://documents.uefa.com/v/u/WVKcnryVkASzztwJjPBcIw|accessdate=11 May 2021|date=9 March 2018|work=UEFA.com|publisher=Union of European Football Associations|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511180320/https://documents.uefa.com/internal/api/webapp/documents/WVKcnryVkASzztwJjPBcIw/content|archivedate=11 May 2021}}</ref>

该赛事原定于2020年6月12日至7月12日举行。但由于[[2019冠状病毒病欧洲疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]，比赛被推迟到2021年6月11日至7月11日。<ref name="postponed">{{Cite news|date=17 March 2020|title=UEFA postpones EURO 2020 by 12 months|work=UEFA.com|publisher=Union of European Football Associations|url=https://www.uefa.com/insideuefa/about-uefa/news/025b-0f8e76aef315-8506a9de10aa-1000/|accessdate=17 March 2020|archive-date=2021-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210611164651/https://www.uefa.com/insideuefa/about-uefa/news/025b-0f8e76aef315-8506a9de10aa-1000/}}</ref>不过保留了「UEFA EURO 2020」（2020年歐洲盃）的名稱不變<ref name="guidelines">{{cite news|url=https://www.uefa.com/insideuefa/news/newsid=2641715.html|title=Executive Committee approves guidelines on eligibility for participation in UEFA competitions|website=UEFA.com|publisher=Union of European Football Associations|date=23 April 2020|accessdate=23 April 2020|archivedate=2020-05-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200523220733/https://www.uefa.com/insideuefa/news/newsid=2641715.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20200424/bkn-20200424021515924-0424_00882_001.html 最後扑槌 明年歐國盃都係叫「EURO2020」] {{Wayback|url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20200424/bkn-20200424021515924-0424_00882_001.html |date=20211003085913 }}，on.cc東網，2020-04-24</ref><ref>[https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/464921/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E7%9B%83-%E8%88%87%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E5%A5%A7%E9%81%8B%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E5%91%BD%E9%81%8B-%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E7%84%A1%E9%A0%88%E6%94%B9%E5%90%8D 【歐洲國家盃】與東京奧運相同命運 押後一年無須改名] {{Wayback|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/464921/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E7%9B%83-%E8%88%87%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E5%A5%A7%E9%81%8B%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E5%91%BD%E9%81%8B-%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E7%84%A1%E9%A0%88%E6%94%B9%E5%90%8D |date=20211005153520 }}，香港01，2020-04-24</ref>。这是史上第一次延後舉行的歐洲盃。<ref>{{Cite web|title=新冠肺炎疫情在欧洲12国蔓延 欧洲杯比奥运会更“悬”|url=http://sports.people.com.cn/n1/2020/0228/c22141-31608635.html|accessdate=2021-06-11|work=人民网|5=|archive-date=2021-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210611140321/http://sports.people.com.cn/n1/2020/0228/c22141-31608635.html}}</ref>

该赛事在11个欧足联成员的11个城市举办，这是为了庆祝歐洲盃60周年。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Croke|first=Ruaidhrí|url=https://www.irishtimes.com/sport/soccer/international/dublin-to-baku-what-s-the-cost-of-euro-2020-for-the-planet-1.4138492|title=Dublin to Baku: What's the cost of Euro 2020 for the planet?|work=[[The_Irish_Times|The Irish Times]]|date=14 January 2020|accessdate=22 June 2020|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028154733/https://www.irishtimes.com/sport/soccer/international/dublin-to-baku-what-s-the-cost-of-euro-2020-for-the-planet-1.4138492}}</ref>这也成为了史上最多國家主辦的單一賽事。<ref>{{cite news|author=WOWSight|title=《足球》歐國盃12日開踢|url=https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%83-%E6%AD%90%E5%9C%8B%E7%9B%8312%E6%97%A5%E9%96%8B%E8%B8%A2-eleven%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%E5%AE%B6%E6%97%8F%E5%85%A8%E5%8F%B0%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E8%BD%89%E6%92%AD-100725605.html|accessdate=2021-06-11|publisher=雅虎|date=2021-06-04|archive-date=2021-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210611140324/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%83-%E6%AD%90%E5%9C%8B%E7%9B%8312%E6%97%A5%E9%96%8B%E8%B8%A2-eleven%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%E5%AE%B6%E6%97%8F%E5%85%A8%E5%8F%B0%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E8%BD%89%E6%92%AD-100725605.html}}</ref>[[伦敦|伦敦]][[温布利球场|温布利球场]]是所有参赛体育场馆中[[座位数|容量]]最大的，它将举办本届赛事的[[#準決賽|半决赛]]和[[#決賽|决赛]]。[[罗马|罗马]]的[[羅馬奧林匹克體育場|奥林匹克体育场]]被选为开幕式和首场比赛的举办地。最初计划由[[#比賽球場|13个场馆]]承办所有比赛，后来有两个场馆（[[布鲁塞尔-首都大区|布鲁塞尔]]的[[欧洲体育场_(比利时)|欧洲体育场]]由于建设延迟，<ref name="opening match">{{Cite news|url=https://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro-2020/news/newsid=2525102.html|title=EURO 2020 to open in Rome, more London games, venues paired|work=UEFA.com|publisher=Union of European Football Associations|date=7 December 2017|accessdate=7 December 2017|archive-date=2019-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190528062850/https://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro-2020/news/newsid=2525102.html}}</ref>[[都柏林|都柏林]]由于疫情期间无法保证观众可入场）被取消承办权，[[毕尔巴鄂|毕尔巴鄂]]的比赛被改到[[塞维利亚|塞维利亚]]进行。<ref name="change of venues">{{Cite news|url=https://www.uefa.com/insideuefa/mediaservices/mediareleases/news/0268-121bc78c82d5-1ba16401b4f0-1000/|title=Change of venues for some UEFA EURO 2020 matches announced|work=UEFA|date=23 April 2021|accessdate=23 April 2021|archive-date=2021-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210611144724/https://www.uefa.com/insideuefa/mediaservices/mediareleases/news/0268-121bc78c82d5-1ba16401b4f0-1000/}}</ref>

[[葡萄牙國家足球隊|葡萄牙队]]是本屆的卫冕冠军。本届欧洲杯是第一届使用[[視頻助理裁判|视频助理裁判（VAR）系统]]的欧洲杯。<ref name="VAR">{{Cite news|date=27 September 2018|title=VAR to be introduced in 2019/20 UEFA Champions League|work=UEFA.com|publisher=Union of European Football Associations|url=https://www.uefa.com/insideuefa/about-uefa/news/0250-0c5119ff28b2-feda7fc5c929-1000--var-to-be-introduced-in-2019-20-uefa-champions-league/|accessdate=27 September 2018|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809030530/https://www.uefa.com/insideuefa/about-uefa/news/0250-0c5119ff28b2-feda7fc5c929-1000--var-to-be-introduced-in-2019-20-uefa-champions-league/}}</ref>

