== 营销和周边 ==
=== 标志和口号 ===
官方标志于2016年9月21日在[[伦敦|伦敦]][[倫敦市政廳_(南華克)|市政厅]]举行的仪式上揭晓。该标志描绘了欧洲杯的亨利·德劳内奖杯在一座桥上被庆祝的球迷包围的情景。根据欧足联的说法，这代表了足球如何连接和团结了人们。<ref>{{Cite news|date=20 September 2016|title=UEFA EURO 2020 logo unveiled|work=UEFA.com|publisher=Union of European Football Associations|url=https://www.uefa.com/insideuefa/mediaservices/news/0253-0d81b6ea20f8-672f1f20c3e2-1000--uefa-euro-2020-logo-unveiled/|accessdate=25 September 2019|archive-date=2020-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731190307/https://www.uefa.com/insideuefa/mediaservices/news/0253-0d81b6ea20f8-672f1f20c3e2-1000--uefa-euro-2020-logo-unveiled/}}</ref><ref name="london">{{Cite news|author=Tarn|first=Sam|location=London|url=https://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro-2020/news/newsid=2406718.html|title=UEFA EURO 2020 identity revealed in London|work=UEFA.com|publisher=Union of European Football Associations|date=21 September 2016|accessdate=25 September 2019|archive-date=2018-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180607175527/http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro-2020/news/newsid=2406718.html}}</ref>

每个主办城市也有自己的标志：矩形标志的顶部是“UEFA EURO 2020”文字，底部是全部为大写的城市名称和“HOST CITY”的字样，中间左侧是2020年欧洲杯的标志，右侧是当地的标志性桥梁。每个徽标均以英文显示，需要时可使用当地语言进行更改。这些标志于 2016年9月至2017年1月公布。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Corda|first=Francesco|url=https://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro-2020/news/newsid=2407265.html|title=Rome unveils UEFA EURO 2020 host city logo|work=UEFA.com|publisher=Union of European Football Associations|date=22 September 2016|accessdate=25 September 2019|archive-date=2017-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170724045450/http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro-2020/news/newsid=2407265.html}}</ref>

比赛的官方口号是“Live It. For Real”（大致上可译为“真实体验”），旨在鼓励球迷到现场观看比赛。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.uefa.com/insideuefa/mediaservices/mediareleases/newsid=2605409.html|title=LIVE IT. FOR REAL: Attractive ticket offer for UEFA EURO 2020|work=UEFA.com|publisher=Union of European Football Associations|date=19 May 2019|accessdate=25 September 2019|archive-date=2019-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191109031736/https://www.uefa.com/insideuefa/mediaservices/mediareleases/newsid=2605409.html}}</ref>

=== 比赛用球 ===
{{main|Uniforia}}
[[File:4-adidas-euro-2020-ball-min.jpg|缩略图]]
2019年11月6日，欧足联宣布[[阿迪达斯|阿迪达斯]]的“Uniforia”将成为赛事的官方比赛用球。球以白色为主，带有黑色粗线和蓝色、霓虹和粉红色线条。“Uniforia”是“团结”（unity）和“欣快感”（euphoria）的[[混成詞|混成詞]]。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.uefa.com/insideuefa/news/newsid=2630585.html|title=adidas unveils Uniforia official match ball for UEFA EURO 2020|work=UEFA.com|publisher=Union of European Football Associations|date=6 November 2019|accessdate=6 November 2019|archive-date=2020-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516124533/https://www.uefa.com/insideuefa/news/newsid=2630585.html}}</ref>

